3. Run the streaming programs on AWS EMR
Cluster Configuration:
Log folder S3 location: s3://xli862014/log/

Software Configuration:
Hadoop distribution: Amazon
AMI version: 2.4.2(hadoop 1.0.3) - latest
Applications to be installed: none

EC2 instance types and counts: 
Master: m1.medium, Count 1
Core: m1.medium, Count 4
Task: Count 0

Steps:
Streaming Program:
Mapper: s3://xli862014/codes/trianglecount.mapper.py
Reducer: s3://xli862014/codes/trianglecount.reducer.py
Input S3 location: s3://xli862014/friends1000/
Output S3 location: s3://xli862014/output/streaming1000/
Arguments: None
Action on failure: Continue
--------------------------------------------------------
